    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Letters, symbols, or ornament tranferred from a backing sheet to a working surface, either by burnishing or by hand placement of cut-out self-adhesive characters and figures.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
